OL,5,MTildagon 2026: Spaceagon
OL,7,GTwo years ago, we released the
OL,8,GTildagon - a new approach to camp
OL,9,Gbadges, designed to be reused and
OL,10,Gupgraded at several future EMF events
OL,11,Grather than abandoned in a drawer.
OL,12,GKeeping our promise, the 2026 Tildagon
OL,13,Ghas a new front board to match the
OL,14,G“space” theme, along with the first
OL,15,Gofficial hexpansion to add new
OL,16,Gcapabilities. All of these upgrades
OL,17,Gare available to order now. We call it
OL,18,Gthe Spaceagon. This is a prototype
OL,19,Gwith prototype artwork - the final
OL,20,Gdesign will be revealed in the field.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
